  "description": "AC-Coupled Instrumentation Amplifier (Bridge/Sensor Front-End). 3-op-amp INA, single-supply + Vref, input AC-coupled. Tầng 1-2: U1,U2 non-inverting với RG chung (gain = 1+2R1/RG). Tầng 3: U3 diff amp (R3,R4 input, R5 feedback, R6 ref→VREF). VREF tạo bởi RVREF1,RVREF2. BOM: 7R (R1,R2,RG,R3,R4,R5,R6) + 2R (RVREF1,RVREF2) + 2C (CINP,CINN) = 9R + 2C.",
